  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Plant Technician",
  "description": "<p>Location of plant: Ang Mo Kio / Benoi / Jurong Island</p>\n<p>Working Hours: 0830 - 1730</p>\n<p>Working Days: Monday - Friday</p>\n<p>Annual Leave: 7</p>\n<p>Job Scope:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Operation and maintenance of Wastewater treatment plant (WWTP)</li>\n  <li>Daily performance log management of WWTP Plant;</li>\n  <li>Daily monitoring of plant performance;</li>\n  <li>Preventive maintenance of mechanical equipment;</li>\n  <li>Preventive maintenance of electrical and Instruments;</li>\n  <li>Electrical &amp; Instruments Component Health check;</li>\n  <li>Daily chemical top up and maintain the correct level;</li>\n  <li>Daily reporting to management of plant performance;</li>\n  <li>Calibration of Instruments as per schedule;</li>\n  <li>Ensure WWTP compliance with ISO standards;</li>\n  <li>Control and Monitoring system review;</li>\n  <li>Conduct daily housekeeping and 5s;</li>\n  <li>Conduct minor maintenance (bi-monthly) and major maintenance (bi-annually)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Preferred with personal transport</p>\n<p>Allowance for petrol and travel</p>",
